      "content": "Hey, we have a problem. One of the reporters from the Chronicle just called—they saw the candidate's speech today and they're already drafting a piece about how he's completely reversed his position on the Tax Act compared to what he said last month. Our sentiment trackers are starting to dip. How should we handle this? We can't afford for the press to start calling him a flip-flopper right now.",
